Blue Block Free Privacy Policy
Aragosoft Inc ("us", "we", or "our") operates the "Blue Block" mobile games.
This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.
What We Collect
We do not collect personal information on this website or within the app.
The app uses advertising (and in app payments) to make revenue. The app uses third party libraries for advertising which may collect and share personal information with third parties.
Privacy policies of third party service providers used in the app
AdMob : https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. Thus, we advise you to review this page periodically for any changes. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.
